      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '<size=42><b>AR Fire Escape</b></size>


        This scene demonstrates
        use of the AR in fire escape scenario. Close the <color=yellow>door </color>
        and walk out of the room to contain the fire. Wear the fire vest and turn
        on the sprinklers if they are not active.


        <size="32"><b>Close Door</b></size>

        DialogLarge_192x192.prefab

        DialogMedium_192x128

        DialogSmall_192x96.prefab


        <size="32"><b>Wear
        Vest</b></size>

        Image Targets are used to identify user actions.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
